-- Multiple Injuries in Shooting at Denver Movie Theater, KOA Says
-- B y   C h r i s   P e t e r s o n
-- 2012-07-20T08:26:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-20/multiple-injuries-in-shooting-at-denver-movie-theater-koa-says.html
As many as 30 to 40 people were
injured in a shooting incident at the Century Theater in the
Aurora Mall in Denver, Colorado, KOA Radio station reported,
citing police communications.  Witness said a smoke or tear gas bomb was set off by a
person wearing a gas mask, the local radio station said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
